data.description: Located in the highly desired Cactus-Shea corridor, this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is located on the large corner lot of a cul-de-sac street. Open kitchen with tons of cabinets and counter space. The large primary bedroom offers a separate tub and shower, double sinks and a massive walk-in closet. Main areas of the home have vaulted ceilings, architectural touches and plant shelves.2- car garage with attached cabinets and utility sink. Beautiful backyard with covered patio and low-maintenance landscaping. Great shopping and dining nearby, close to Cholla Park with Pickle Ball courts, volleyball, and playgrounds.
